na_skill.name: Virtuous Compassion
na_skill.raw_description: Reduces bind status (incl. Awoken) by 3 turns; changes all Orbs to Wood, Dark & Heal Orbs

params: Voids status ailments for a number of turns
Absorbs attacks of 8 combos or fewer for 5 turns
